Data Models (schemas)
- UserProfile
  - id, user_id, firstName, lastName, displayName, email, avatarUrl, phone, createdAt, updatedAt
- UserPreference
  - user_id, preferences: {
      autopilotEnabled: boolean,
      defaultAgent: string,
      notificationPrefs: { email: boolean, sms: boolean, push: boolean },
      dataExportConsent: boolean,
      // additional module toggles
    }, updatedAt
- Integration
  - id, user_id, provider: string, status: 'connected'|'disconnected'|'error', lastSyncedAt, credentialsRef
- ApiKey
  - id, user_id, keyHash, scopes: string[], name, createdAt, lastUsedAt, revocable: boolean
- Billing
  - id, user_id, planId, planName, seats, renewalDate, invoices: [{ id, amount, date, url }]
- Session
  - id, user_id, device, ip, startedAt, lastActiveAt, expiresAt, revoked: boolean
- 2FA
  - id, user_id, method: 'totp'|'fido2'|'sms', enabled: boolean, details

