- Authentication: JWT-based sessions, OAuth, SSO integration points
- Authorization: RBAC checks for sensitive actions (API key creation, 2FA changes, billing changes)
- Data protection: Credentials encrypted at rest; credentials referenced; rotation policies
- Input validation: strong server-side validation; reject invalid scopes or providers
